<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，雪莉老师。今天我们要做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森第一个来到儿童中心活动的体育馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，贾森。等大家都到了我才能告诉你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，你可以先帮我发这些卡片。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好。” 尼娜走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡片是拿来做什么的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都到了才能知道。” 贾森告诉她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比和莉琪走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们开始吧！” 贾森对雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都到了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，我还没准备好呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪看了看尼娜，坐在桌子旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我准备好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要做一件不可能做到的事。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不可能！” 波比说。大家哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿起你的卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是卡片大，还是你的脸大？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的脸。” 莉琪和尼娜同时说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然是我的脸。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，贾森摇摇头。他看过魔术表演。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个陷阱问题吗？” 贾森问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得卡片比较大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得卡片比较大？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们来量一量吧。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡片有多大呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比量了量。“长13厘米，宽8厘米。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你量过自己的脸吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的脸长17厘米，宽12厘米。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以你的脸比较大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我可以让你的头穿过这个小卡片。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起她的卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？不可能！” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不可能。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师一定可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪看着自己最喜欢的老师，笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要给你们看一个小招数。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是魔术吗？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是魔术，是小招数。” 她回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第一步：把卡片上下对折。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二步：在卡片一边剪13刀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都小心地剪着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第三步：在另外一边剪13刀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第四步：小心地打开卡片，沿着中间的折痕剪开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，不要剪开第一个和最后一个折痕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>变成什么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森打开卡片。他的眼睛睁大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！真大。我的头可以穿过去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但它还是一个普通的卡片。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把她的卡片合起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个招数真酷，雪莉老师。” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您可以教我们更多的招数吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。但是现在你爸爸在等你了。” 她指了指门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸！” 贾森跳起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想看一个很酷的招数吗？我可以把头穿过卡片！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>